1
00:00:01,659 --> 00:00:02,720
Hello, friend.

2
00:00:04,740 --> 00:00:06,120
Hello, hello, buddy.

3
00:00:06,860 --> 00:00:08,619
Şükran, come sit next to Şüray for a moment.

4
00:00:08,939 --> 00:00:09,480
All right, sir.

5
00:00:11,119 --> 00:00:11,720
What's up?

6
00:00:12,279 --> 00:00:14,199
No, sir, not even a drop of water—we don’t want any.

7
00:00:14,679 --> 00:00:15,980
There's a pair of pants there.

8
00:00:16,300 --> 00:00:17,780
The pipe is yours now—congratulations.

9
00:00:18,320 --> 00:00:21,079
We have nothing to do with the water; it’s because of my brother.

10
00:00:21,420 --> 00:00:22,019
Are you free?

11
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:23,899
So, do I belong here?

12
00:00:24,219 --> 00:00:24,899
It's in my pocket.

13
00:00:25,759 --> 00:00:27,239
What kind of plow should we use?

14
00:00:27,620 --> 00:00:28,699
You saw us in the garden.

15
00:00:29,140 --> 00:00:30,140
Did you think he was a gardener?

16
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:31,920
I am Özgür, my driver.

17
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:33,460
Wise, wise.

18
00:00:33,859 --> 00:00:36,679
I also remember the world middleweight boxing champion.

19
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:37,700
It's a mistake.

20
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:39,939
That looks nice.

